ACQURING DATA:
*NOTE* it is recommended that you use firefox, and install the free plugin "DwonThemAll" for easier bulk downloading. 
Go to http://ursa.asfdaac.alaska.edu
Select search & order tab on left-hand side  --> Geographic search
Submit search location request (1)
  By expanding with "show more options", can select point search with a circle, but any search parameters are fine. 
Select ALOS PALSAR (2), by opening "more options"
  Select FBD and FBS beam modes
  Leave Faraday rotation at "ANY"
  Select an off nadir angle of 34.3
Leave date range in (3)
Leave selections in (4)
Hit "submit search"


